{"title":"铁盘整理","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2524","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>在训练中一些臂力训练器材是少不了的小龙在练习的时候发现举重器械上的铁盘放置的非常混乱并没有按照从轻到重的顺序摆放这样非常不利于循序渐进的锻炼。他打算利用一个非常省力气的办法来整理这些铁盘即每次都拿起最上面的若干个圆盘并利用器械的力量上下翻转这样翻转若干次以后铁盘将会按照从小到大的顺序排列好。那么你能不能帮小龙确定最少翻转几次就可以使铁盘按从小到大排序呢</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>共两行第一行为铁盘个数N 1≤N≤50。第二行为N个不同的正整数中间用空格分开分别为从上到下的铁盘的半径R 1≤R≤100。 </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个正整数 表示使铁盘按从小到大有序需要的最少翻转次数。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">5</span></p>\n<p>2 4 3 5 1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>见题面</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}